        "last_activity_date": 1527396636,
        "creation_date": 1527396636,
        "body": "<p>You can use a <code>FactoryBean<\/code> to receive all the arguments to your irregular class and then return it from the <code>getObject()<\/code> method.<\/p>\n\n<p>See <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3236850/spring-using-builder-pattern-to-create-a-bean\">this question<\/a>.<\/p>\n",
